events.text:
General Laws:
1 - NO WEAPONS.
2 - DO NOT ATTEMPT TO SPEAK TO THE LOCALS.
3 - IF A LOCAL SPEAKS TO YOU CONTACT A PADVA INFORCER.
4 - IF STAYING FOR PROLONGED PERIODS, CONTACT GENERAL MICHAEL.
5 - IF STAYING FOR SHORT PERIOD, YOU MUST LEAVE BY 8PM.
6 - PADVA INFORCERS MAY STOP YOU FOR ANY REASON AT ALL.
Follow these rules and you'll have a fine time.
I should probably put away this Long Dagger then.
To unequip your weapon or armor, press TAB and type the # of the item you want to unequip.
